   --------------------------------------------------------------------------
     +  +    +        +   The Ministry of Silly Vaults   +        +    +  +
   --------------------------------------------------------------------------

utility scripts that generate vaults presumably for use in a roguelike
plus various other somewhat rogue related code

            ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  ..#..  .###.  .###.  .###.
