    dijkstramap.lisp
    dijkstramap.tex
    dijkstramap.pdf
      random thoughts on pathfinding

    erosion
      corrupts walls using particular methods

        cat board
        ./erosion board

    explorer.lisp
      level map tester, lets you move around a provided board

        sbcl --script explorer.lisp board

    klaji.lisp
      a better street grid generator than corridors.lisp

